user_prompt_template:
Create or upgrade a Forge preset using this input:

PRESET_ID: {preset_id}
PRESET_GOAL: {preset_goal}
PRIMARY_USE: {primary_use}
AUDIENCE: {audience}
CURRENT_PRESET_JSON:
{current_preset_json}
REFERENCE_DESCRIPTIONS:
{reference_descriptions}
KNOWN_FAILURES:
{known_failures}
MUST_KEEP:
{must_keep}

Return only valid JSON matching the requested output schema. The preset must include meaningful semantic tokens and dependency vectors. Every token must be observable in the image, useful for prompt assembly, or useful for evaluation. Every dependency vector must explain why one token requires, supports, conflicts with, or inhibits another token.
